 eshop.com/\nStore Details: https://locator.wizards.com/store/13099\nEvent 
 Details: https://locator.wizards.com/event/10737683\n\nFind your place amo
 ng the five colleges as we put down the books and delve into the real worl
 d! Uncover the Secrets of Strixhaven and prove your college is the best wi
 th every spell you cast. Commander Party is a casual event that introduces
  a new way to experience the fan favorite format with thematic and flavorf
 ul new rules. Each participant will receive a promo for playing. Participa
 tion will be on a first come first serve basis. We can't wait to see you t
 here!\nSource: wizards-locator
